Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-tk, ifuse, libimobiledevice-utils, usbmuxd, fuse
Description: iPhone File Transfer Utility for Linux
 PlugNPass (pronounced "Plug and Pass") is a user-friendly
 utility for transferring files between Linux computers 
 and iOS devices (iPhone, iPad).
 .
 Features:
  * Media Access: Browse and download photos, videos, and music
  * Document Transfer: Upload and download files to/from app folders
  * Multiple File Support: Select and download multiple files at once
  * File Filtering: Automatically hides system files
  * Search: Easily find files by name 